description:
This is a 14 minute workout called 'The Best Calisthenics Exercises For Each Muscle' from the channel THENX.
The workout falls under Strength/Calisthenics and Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Advanced and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Masterclass Workout and The Progression Quest vibe.
The technique difficulty is Advanced and Expert.
The effort required is Challenging.
